  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to evaluate the quality of care provided by a home-based teleheath program as
      a safe and acceptable alternative to an in-person office visit as determined by satisfaction
      with the program and the amount of further medical management required by the patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
